HEADWORD: Reentering
<hw>Re*en"ter*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Calico Printing.)</fld>
<def>The process of applying additional colors, by applications of
printing blocks, to patterns already partly colored.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

